    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings that house prisons populated by prisoners who can be reasonably trusted to not to try to escape; the term is often used in British prison systems.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
